{"tid":469241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"濃霧肇禍！中國驚爆30車連環撞 數車起火燒成焦殼","createTime":"2017-11-15T06:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T16:09:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"10ac0ba7b30075f1f49a0cd1f708c91b31dbeba4","tid":469241,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510719465_fab8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510719465_fab8.jpg&h=986b0e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國安徽今（15日）上午發生超過30輛車連環追撞的嚴重車禍，現場有4輛大小車輛起火燒成焦殼，目前已傳出有人員死亡，至於實際傷亡數字仍待救難行動告一段落後方可得知。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，這起連環車禍發生在滁新高速公路安徽阜陽段，今上午8時許該路段起了濃霧，疑受此影響，共有超過30台大小車輛發生追撞，更有2輛自小客車、大貨車及水泥槽罐車等4輛車起火，火勢一度十分猛烈。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，警消人員立即趕往現場搶救，將火勢順利撲滅，據消防單位表示，截至上午11時已救出17人，但也有民眾不幸罹難，遺體被救護人員暫時以白布包裹。據悉，消防人員目前仍於現場實施救援，至於本起事故的具體傷亡數字仍待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2254264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2254264&d=sN1xzYXJtnc%2F%2F0sNkt83G%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=37162551\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2254264&h=eec84f1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2254264</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510719464_d155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510719464_d155.jpg&h=29b3d139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510719463_42a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510719463_42a7.jpg&h=aad2a641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510719463_78a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510719463_78a0.jpg&h=2ed75990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510719615_2022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510719615_2022.jpg&h=28030b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171115/57460443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460443&d=sN1xzYXJtnc%2F%2F0sNkt83G%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=46acc31c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460443&h=0e1c3d5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171115/57460443</a>"},{"pid":"d1be7f1cf2e22e05149f7d1760a65dd13a325d8d","tid":469241,"uid":1582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"30車咁少"},{"pid":"774b436d73c7b7c09c905f75a0ff719239b3b300","tid":469241,"uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"巴士燒剩架細車變「杮餅」 目擊網民：好恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510721520_0686.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510721520_0686.jpg&h=3caf7efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510720981_0af3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510720981_0af3.jpg&h=712b4c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510720982_b194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510720982_b194.jpg&h=f20945fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滁新高速安徽阜陽段今早8時許發生嚴重車禍，逾30部車連環追撞，其中4部車起火，當中包括兩部巴士，不少私家車則被夾在大車之間，變成「杮餅」。有目擊者po照貼文，大呼恐怖，稱「兩輛大客車（巴士）燒得剩空殼了」，傷者則在路邊等候救援，疑似有人傷重不治，被搬到路邊，蓋上白布，但當局至今仍未公佈死傷情況。<br />\n<br />\n有當地人稱，今早十分大霧，交警已經在高速公路實施臨時交通管制，分流疏導車輛，不過仍沒法避免嚴重車禍的發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171115/57460506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460506&d=sN1xzYXJtnc%2F%2F0sNkt83G%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=2e6ec414\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460506&h=071eb808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171115/57460506</a>"},{"pid":"1d3038902c242f8f89d132205afb2506b0241d84","tid":469241,"uid":36178,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"懷念津爆"},{"pid":"e99ace77c270d19fee679447b8898a98b8af5439","tid":469241,"uid":59929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"肯定冇人死啦<br />\n唔準亂咁傳遙言"},{"pid":"8af79d2f29250bf272a7eb1bd6d2ba1ab48cea63","tid":469241,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8ff2b325b49ad09b23143936d37718a2235648","tid":469241,"uid":17718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"點做到"},{"pid":"6d05570b77796d0835ae0e56ba9267e646ba4be1","tid":469241,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:33:04.000Z",